            </div>

            <div class="security-note">
                <strong>ðŸ”’ Security Tip:</strong> Keep your login credentials secure and never share them with anyone.
                If you suspect unauthorized access, contact our support team immediately.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="email-footer">
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="<%= helpUrl %>">Help Center</a>
                <a href="<%= trackingUrl %>">Track Package</a>
                <a href="<%= supportUrl %>">Contact Support</a>
            </div>
            <p class="footer-text">Â© 2025 SendIT. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p class="footer-text">You're receiving this email because you created an account with SendIT.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>